high_descs: Go straight and turn left to the fridge.
Pick the kettle from the fridge.
Turn around and head to the sink.
Put the kettle in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn left and move to the counter.
Place the kettle on the counter.

Put the kettle on the counter top
